snippet.title: For Better, For Worse | Arise With Amber
snippet.description:
New Arise With Amber episodes launch every Sunday at 8am CST!
New Smiths episodes launch every Tuesday and Thursday at 6pm CST!
Shop Yee Yee Apparel ►  https://YeeYeeApparel.com/

Songs of worship I listen to ► https://open.spotify.com/playlist/61O2osrqapoo6K8iH2soIQ?si=B5KmQgzfTcmgr5ABkfskQg
Visit the River Kelly Fund Website here► https://www.riverkellyfund.org/

"That's Why I Love Dirt Roads" Music Video► https://youtu.be/UvlWF4g8XA0
Listen to Granger's new song here► https://grangersmith.lnk.to/dirtroads
Tickets to Granger's Tour► https://GrangerSmith.com/tour

We moved our petition to a new site. Please use this link to sign for River and to help save the lives of other children in your life. Thank you so much ► https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/rivers-law-save-lives-require-all-homeowners-have-4-sided-4-foot-self-latching-pool-gates-pool-alarms

About this channel: We are the Smith's. A family of 5, living in the country just outside of Georgetown, Texas. Granger, a touring country music singer, Amber, an actor and stay at home mom, and their children: London, Lincoln and River.
